  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chorus of Carcosa is a psychological horror game inspired by the classic horror fiction of 'The King in Yellow' collection by R. W. Chambers. You play as a sculptor who is forced to abandon his place of comfort one night, when a blood-soaked neighbor knocks on his door.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1743606513\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span><strong>KEY FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around two-three hours of classic horror thriller gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless tension — finding a way out is no easy task </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple stealth mechanics — try to remain unnoticed when there’s no place to hide</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive graphics and high-quality 3D sound powered by Unreal Engine 5</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully written, directed, and voiced by professional actors</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience the fear of facing the unknown </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive an ever-changing decrepit apartment building filled with dangers and mysteries... Without making a sound! Or THEY will hear you…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve the mystery of an alternate reality</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A twisted realm fills the space around you. Are all of these changes real? Or are they just nightmarish hallucinations?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You can flee, but escape is an illusion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They have found you and there's no turning back now. Perhaps, it’s sometimes wiser to embrace the surrounding madness and stare right back into its eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1743606513\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chorus of Carcosa is a psychological horror game inspired by the classic horror fiction of 'The King in Yellow' collection by R. W. Chambers. You play as a sculptor who is forced to abandon his place of comfort one night, when a blood-soaked neighbor knocks on his door.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1743606513\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span><strong>KEY FEATURES </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around two-three hours of classic horror thriller gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless tension — finding a way out is no easy task </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple stealth mechanics — try to remain unnoticed when there’s no place to hide</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive graphics and high-quality 3D sound powered by Unreal Engine 5</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully written, directed, and voiced by professional actors</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience the fear of facing the unknown </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive an ever-changing decrepit apartment building filled with dangers and mysteries... Without making a sound! Or THEY will hear you…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/05c95659de16d850bb38467242a5dc8c.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve the mystery of an alternate reality</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A twisted realm fills the space around you. Are all of these changes real? Or are they just nightmarish hallucinations?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/95c849dd83c35a30cfbf8ad338b61507.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You can flee, but escape is an illusion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They have found you and there's no turning back now. Perhaps, it’s sometimes wiser to embrace the surrounding madness and stare right back into its eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.webm?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/f9e26acaddc54a952a5f73765c0cb76c.mp4?t=1743606513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.webp?t=1743606513\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987750/extras/caff2bb7f29dbe3252d74befa5d63b65.poster.avif?t=1743606513\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=33 /></picture></span></p>",
